			[1267] heading 'What is gulp?'
			[1269] list ''
				[1270] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					[1271] strong ''
						StaticText 'Automation'
					StaticText '- gulp is a toolkit that helps you automate painful or time-consuming tasks in your development workflow.'
				[1272] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					[1273] strong ''
						StaticText 'Platform-agnostic'
					StaticText '- Integrations are built into all major IDEs and people are using gulp with PHP, .NET, Node.js, Java, and other platforms.'
				[1274] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					[1275] strong ''
						StaticText 'Strong Ecosystem'
					StaticText '- Use npm modules to do anything you want + over 3000 curated plugins for streaming file transformations.'
				[1276] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					[1277] strong ''
						StaticText 'Simple'
					StaticText '- By providing only a minimal API surface, gulp is easy to learn and simple to use.'
			[1278] heading "What's new in 4.0?!"
			[1280] list ''
				[1281] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					StaticText 'The task system was rewritten from the ground-up, allowing task composition using'
					[1282] code ''
						StaticText 'series()'
					StaticText 'and'
					[1283] code ''
						StaticText 'parallel()'
					StaticText 'methods.'
				[1284] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					StaticText 'The watcher was updated, now using chokidar (no more need for gulp-watch!), with feature parity to our task system.'
				[1285] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					StaticText 'First-class support was added for incremental builds using'
					[1286] code ''
						StaticText 'lastRun()'
					StaticText '.'
				[1287] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					StaticText 'A'
					[1288] code ''
						StaticText 'symlink()'
					StaticText 'method was exposed to create symlinks instead of copying files.'
				[1289] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					StaticText 'Built-in support for sourcemaps was added - the gulp-sourcemaps plugin is no longer necessary!'
				[1290] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					StaticText 'Task registration of exported functions - using node or ES exports - is now recommended.'
				[1291] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					StaticText 'Custom registries were designed, allowing for shared tasks or augmented functionality.'
				[1292] listitem ''
					ListMarker '•'
					StaticText 'Stream implementations were improved, allowing for better conditional and phased builds.'
